    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine is strong and responsive, and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a reliable and comfortable driving experience. While there may be minor signs of regular use, the interior is clean and the exterior has been well-preserved. It is a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned car that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
